properties.name: dialogue
properties.value:
Confusion is a self-fulfilled prophecy, a state of mind caused by the lack of will and a product of cowardice.
Every mind problem can be fixed by the mind itself because after all
it is through the mind that we experience reality and therefore reality is defined by it
You know exactly what you feel, what you think and who you are
but it's all just buried deep below the safe space you've created to shield yourself from outside criticism
thoughts like me won't dissapear until you do something about it
